   <concept id="FAR_3_603" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">3.603</ph> Responsibilities of the contracting officer.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d129e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d131e10">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
						            Before awarding a contract, the contracting officer shall obtain an authorization under <xref href="3.602.dita#FAR_3_602"
                        base="i1124277"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">3.602</xref> if-</p>
               <ol id="d129e26" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d131e19">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
								                The contracting officer knows, or has reason to believe, that a prospective contractor is one to which award is otherwise prohibited under <xref href="3.601.dita#FAR_3_601"
                              base="i1124266"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">3.601</xref>; and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d131e27">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
								                There is a most compelling reason to make an award to that prospective contractor.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d131e32">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
						            The contracting officer shall comply with the requirements and guidance in <xref href="Subpart_9.5.dita#FAR_Subpart_9_5"
                        base="i1114943"
                        outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                        class="- topic/xref ">subpartÂ  9.5</xref> before awarding a contract to an organization owned or substantially owned or controlled by Government employees.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
